openVpnConfig.config:
client
proto udp
remote usa1.vpnjantit.com 2500
resolv-retry infinite
nobind
persist-key
persist-tun
remote-cert-tls server
verb 3
<ca>
...CA certificate...
</ca>
<cert>
...Client certificate...
</cert>
<key>
...Private key...
</key>
key-direction 1
<tls-auth>
...Static key...
</tls-auth>
